name: Alliance Tournament IX: HYDRA RELOADED and 0utbreak
description: After a bitter finals defeat the previous year, <url=showinfo:16159//551692893>HYDRA RELOADED</url> entered the Ninth Alliance Tournament with something to prove. They played the field and metagame masterfully, shrugging aside all their opponents and ensuring a first-second place finish for themselves and their close allies in <url=showinfo:16159//99000648>Outbreak.</url>. A botched attempt to put on a show finals created controversy and forced changes to future Tournament rules, but the skill and dedication of the pilots in these two alliances was undeniable.
group_name: Tournament Cards: Alliance Tournament All Stars
